Package de.hsrt.holbox.playground

Class HybridPowerPlantExample

java.lang.Object
de.hsrt.holbox.playground.HybridPowerPlantExample
public class HybridPowerPlantExample extends Object
This class implements a simple hybrid wind park based on Paper by E. Muljadi: Method of Equivalencing for a Large Wind Power Plant with Multiple Turbine Representation NREL/CP-500-42886
Author:
notholt
